name: EpicBabyNames
0:
”Alexa, open epic baby names”
”Open epic baby names for a boy”
”Open epic baby names for a girl”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: epic baby names
des: A skill that creates an epic name for your baby. You will be asked about the gender of the baby (boy, girl or unknown) and their morals (good or evil). Using that information this skill will determine the legendary name your baby will be known by throughout the world.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
